	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under Q. Servilius at Asculum and was slain there with his commander either late in 91 or early in 90 (Cic. Font. 41 and 48; Vell. 2.15.1; App. BC 1.38; cf. Diod. 37.13.2; Liv. Per. 72; Flor. 2.6.9; Oros. 5.18.8)." .
